trans-unit.source: Enumerates <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Media3D.GeneralTransform3D"></xref> items in a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Media3D.GeneralTransform3DCollection"></xref>.
<xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.GeneralTransform3DCollection.Enumerator> is introduced in the .NET Framework version 3.5.
For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
Gets the current element in the collection.
<xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.GeneralTransform3DCollection.Enumerator.Current%2A> is introduced in the .NET Framework version 3.5.
For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
The current element in the collection.
Advances the enumerator to the next element in the collection.
This method also returns `false` if the enumerator has passed the final element in the collection.
<xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.GeneralTransform3DCollection.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> is introduced in the .NET Framework version 3.5.
For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
`true` if the enumerator successfully advances to the next element; otherwise, `false`.
Resets the enumerator to its initial position, which is before the first element in the collection.
<xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.GeneralTransform3DCollection.Enumerator.Reset%2A> is introduced in the .NET Framework version 3.5.
For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
For a description of this member, see <xref href="System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current"></xref>.
This member is an explicit interface member implementation.
It can be used only when the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.GeneralTransform3DCollection.Enumerator> instance is cast to an <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> interface.
<xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.GeneralTransform3DCollection.Enumerator.System%23Collections%23IEnumerator%23Current%2A> is introduced in the .NET Framework version 3.5.
For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
For a description of this member, see <xref href="System.IDisposable.Dispose"></xref>.
This member is an explicit interface member implementation.
It can be used only when the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.GeneralTransform3DCollection.Enumerator> instance is cast to an <xref:System.IDisposable> interface.
<xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.GeneralTransform3DCollection.Enumerator.System%23IDisposable%23Dispose%2A> is introduced in the .NET Framework version 3.5.
For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
